A vintage-style illustration of a small, cute computer (resembling a Mac Mini) sitting on a wooden desk, with an orange fox curled around it protectively while a steaming coffee cup with the Ubuntu orange circle logo sits nearby. The scene is bathed in warm amber and brown tones reminiscent of 1970s technical manuals, with subtle halftone dot patterns in the background. Scattered around the desk are tiny puzzle pieces in orange, red, and brown colors, some connected and some loose, suggesting troubleshooting and problem-solving. The aesthetic captures the cozy, DIY spirit of early Linux tinkering with a nostalgic warmth.
